{"tid":1134160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【五一巷戰】土瓜灣大廈門外堆起沙包阻遊客坐立","createTime":"2019-05-01T15:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:32:22.000Z","uid":36901,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2c21934052c2ebf0c0c24692a20b7e6e56bb9c","tid":1134160,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=346449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346449&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=50743ead\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346449&h=8da37884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=346449</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大批內地旅客尖沙咀購物擠滿行人路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地五一黃金周大批旅客訪港，除旅行團熱點土瓜灣外，自由行最愛的尖沙咀等購物區都迫滿遊客。<br />\n<br />\n在土瓜灣一間食肆外面，有旅行團團友站在行人路等候進入餐廳吃飯，旁邊的馬路就泊滿旅遊巴。<br />\n<br />\n有上海遊客表示趁五一黃金周假期來港觀光及消費。<br />\n<br />\n區內居民近年已不斷投訴日常生活受影響，黃金周就更頭痛。居民要求商戶控制人流，亦促請政府正視旅客問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">土瓜灣部分住宅大廈門外除了張貼通告提醒遊客這裏是私人地方外，還有加設沙包同欄杆阻止旅客在外面坐立。</span><br />\n<br />\n自由行旅客行程更自由，尖沙咀四處都是內地旅客。廣東道名店已經不是必去，海防道一帶的藥妝店才是旅客目標，拖行李箱掃貨再在店外整理。<br />\n<br />\n行人路水洩不通，部分人要走出馬路，人車爭路，亦有旅客坐在馬路邊，經過的車輛都要留神。<br />\n<br />\n至於鄰近港珠澳大橋香港口岸的東涌，由於很多旅客直接出市區，未見太多人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\novertourism 已經去到打巷戰既地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601f77f2aaf498f1aa8e8de2f1521365561ed0f6","tid":1134160,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班土瓜環居民遲早革命"},{"pid":"23d7d8629307af993948fa5cc94144506dddba61","tid":1134160,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"希望組國同胞多啲關懷香港 振興經濟"},{"pid":"d1d834a1a134b1a0511bbd570607cb9801726ab8","tid":1134160,"uid":159870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:15:45.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣民眾未富先驕"},{"pid":"e1ffef057a38827874b10cbf6137dae1200b7cc8","tid":1134160,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"食碟頭嘅消費條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d19e95e3e34f4dac0c20c66ff93b6231d26e4d","tid":1134160,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCGQT17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCGQT17.jpg&h=0e588ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街坊心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb45b893fc932bd1551e37c661d343a476cf0d74","tid":1134160,"uid":46577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"已經習已為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5900d711cc1804c87209679591dff828b376d9b5","tid":1134160,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"直情要倒水洗街啦！洗走污穢！"},{"pid":"6e16e44ae1bd49cd4760d6f324970b7ac4282a67","tid":1134160,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"上水人心諗:你地班九龍人都有今日啦<br />\n<br />\n利申:不是上水人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb1968fe8246242a54346af696e7c52b6b768ee","tid":1134160,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"果個選民應該搵人話民賤聯工賊會引遊客黎<br />\n<br />\n下次我地派隻豬出去都搶返個位返黎"},{"pid":"e7a422d6a59a9622930792083b230b917e871e5b","tid":1134160,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:31:33.000Z","msg":"侵侵啲牆"},{"pid":"db8042d173e